{
  "stem": "11167.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's killing and hanging, and shooting, and every-- everybody don't know what to do, where to run.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can't go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the borders there came a few young people from Dubno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How they did escape?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they saw the army, and they ran.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's a few of them escaped, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we came to the border, everybody went through, like I told you the story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by me is written as I'm-- my-- my late father was a-- a businessman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't belong to the Communist party to go-- you know, to go through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I gave him some jewelry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I brought an-- lovely watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I say, where must I go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To Hitler?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where must I go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They say that is-- you know, madam, you don't speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you've seen the film, that is that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you say like that with the-- like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They stay, and you can't even come near to-- to explain and to stay as I'm-- I-- my-- my father's already dead when I was a child of 1 year and a 1/2.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That-- not explanation-- that is, there wasn't explanation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- [LAUGHS] --a capitalist with-- with nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- I went to-- I gave him something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, I've got something nice for you or for your wife-- gave him the watch, and I went over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then did started the walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we walk still--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At-- at outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no stay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's not hotels.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's not nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
